  "riddle": "1. Unearth a resting place where history whispers of generations gone by, marked as a national monument — in which year was it officially recognized?\n\n2. What term describes the vibrant cultural group that has flourished across nations, reflected in many languages under their identity?\n\n3. Reflect upon the number of souls who call a land shaped by resilience their home — how many inhabitants reside here?\n\n4. A city once crowned the empire's heart — find the page detailing the one where the Liberty Bell rang through the streets. How many languages echo within its entry?\n\n5. Ascend to the atmospheric heights above this thriving metropolis. What is its ground's elevation in meters?\n\n6. Nearby, how many establishments offering warmth and comfort await travelers seeking rest in this urban hub?\n\n7. The elevation you uncovered and the count of hotels share a story — combine those two numbers for a complete tale.\n\n8. The city buzzes with diverse languages; delve into the binary code of the count you just obtained. How many 1s emerge from its representation?\n\n9. Seek out the stretch of land that cradles culture and community. How many libraries can be found in the embrace of the Atlantic Ocean's shores?\n\n10. Now, the libraries' binary tale holds a secret — extract the number of 1s hidden within its representation.\n\n11. In a borough known for its rich diversity, look for the demographics section. How many subsections contain the tales of its varied peoples?\n\n12. A conflict of great consequence shaped lives in a land of intersecting histories. Calculate the number of days from a pivotal date in 2004 to a significant future moment in 2026.\n\n13. Before completing your quest, resolve the difference between the languages found in clue 4 and the libraries you documented in clue 9, and reduce it using modulo 10. What single digit emerges from this journey?",
